<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>名人 - 人物</title><link>https://siftrss.com/f/LbvpaQbPYJQ</link><description>来自人物的最新名人新闻、采访和故事。</description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 19 Mar 2026 01:11:36 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>泰勒·弗兰基·保罗关于她与前达科塔·莫滕森的法律纠纷所说的一切</title><link>https://people.com/everything-taylor-frankie-paul-has-said-about-her-legal-troubles-11928856</link><description>3月17日，《摩门教妻子的秘密生活》和《单身女郎》明星打破了沉默，对正在进行的家庭暴力调查进行了调查，称这是一个“沉重的时刻” &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://people.com/thmb/rQ3HhGB8d9FZkLuqvOAQyoA5rsc=/filters:no_upscale():max_bytes(150000):strip_icc():format(jpeg)/Taylor-Frankie-Paul-031726-3008af0f234e4097b8565d62ecb6c7d3.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 18 Mar 2026 20:01:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://people.com/everything-taylor-frankie-paul-has-said-about-her-legal-troubles-11928856</guid></item><item><title>《狮子王》歌曲作曲家因歌曲被曲解而向喜剧演员提起 2700 万美元诉讼</title><link>https://people.com/lion-king-chant-composer-files-usd27m-lawsuit-against-comedian-over-song-s-alleged-misinterpretation-11929113</link><description>诉状称，这首歌的作曲家和表演者 Lebo M 正在向喜剧演员 Learnmore Jonasi 寻求 2700 万美元的赔偿&lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://people.com/thmb/cPpNQ5dm21miBjgVk56k1p1oqJY=/filters:no_upscale():max_bytes(150000):strip_icc():format(jpeg)/Lebo-M-Learnmore-Jonasi-031826-79beb668268f4b22a7c10a3acb7bd8ae.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 18 Mar 2026 19:18:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://people.com/lion-king-chant-composer-files-usd27m-lawsuit-against-comedian-over-song-s-alleged-misinterpretation-11929113</guid></item><item><title>《巴菲》校友尼古拉斯·布伦登 (Nicholas Brendon) 被指控在装修其房屋的承包商上贴上 AirTag，请愿者向法庭索赔</title><link>https://people.com/buffy-alum-nicholas-brendon-accused-tracking-contractor-court-filing-11928672</link><description>尼古拉斯·布伦登 (Nicholas Brendon) 此前曾于 2021 年因处方欺诈被捕&lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://people.com/thmb/QzNOgSVW7zsqPrC9f0NWqEOZZ2Q=/filters:no_upscale():max_bytes(150000):strip_icc():format(jpeg)/nicholas-brendon-81a6fd320cbf4571914d20d90128b416.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 18 Mar 2026 16:36:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://people.com/buffy-alum-nicholas-brendon-accused-tracking-contractor-court-filing-11928672</guid></item><item><title>前单身女子迪安娜·帕帕斯在自己的被捕丑闻后为泰勒·弗兰基·保罗辩护：“我去过那里”</title><link>https://people.com/former-bachelorette-deanna-pappas-defends-taylor-frankie-paul-11928777</link><description>帕帕斯在播客上表示，在她的《单身女郎》季首映之前，她为保罗所经历的事情“几乎哭了” &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://people.com/thmb/O0I5moOoL8afVcgrCfnyyzebC-w=/filters:no_upscale():max_bytes(150000):strip_icc():format(jpeg)/deanna-pappas-taylor-frankie-paul-031826-6382fa06219b4aed9c81460ebd2bc8c9.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 18 Mar 2026 16:03:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://people.com/former-bachelorette-deanna-pappas-defends-taylor-frankie-paul-11928777</guid></item></channel></rss>